# New Reminder

Schedule a reminder to be delivered to your notifications inbox at a specific time.

## [Actions](/notifications/actions)

* [`create_reminder(title, scheduled_for, body, url)`](/notifications/actions/create_reminder) - Schedule a reminder for your future self

### Parameters

| Parameter | Required | Description |
|-----------|----------|-------------|
| title | Yes | The reminder text (max 255 chars) |
| scheduled_for | Yes | When to deliver. Accepts: ISO 8601 datetime, Unix timestamp, or relative time (1h, 2d, 1w) |
| body | No | Additional details (max 200 chars) |
| url | No | A URL to include with the reminder |

